Uses of Package
main

  • Packages that use main 
    Package Description
    main
    Contains all the classes required for the game, including the command-line interface and the new GUI interface, as well as helper classes.
    main.animals
    Contains all the different kinds of animals available to the player.
    main.crops
    Contains all the kinds of crops used by the game.
    main.items
    Contains all the kinds of items available to the player.
  • Classes in main used by main 
    Class Description
    Asset
    Basic "asset" that can be purchased or sold in the store, or used by the player on the farm.
    CropCareGUI
    GUI window for tending to crops.
    Farmer
    Handles daily actions made to the farm by the player.
    FarmGUI
    Main GUI window for the farm simulator, with buttons that lead to daily actions or other actions a player can perform.
    FeedingGUI
    GUI window for handling the feeding of item(s) to animals.
    GameManager
    Class that essentially runs the entire GUI game by handling the creation and removal of GUI windows.
    SetupGUI
    GUI window for setting up the player's farm, farmer and game duration.
    StoreGUI
    GUI window for purchasing from the general county store.
